title: O'Neill Girls Freeride Coachings presented by K2 & Blue Tomato.
description:
http://www.oneill.com
The Kitzsteinhorn in Austria welcomed 15 Girls to the freeride season! 
Together with certified mountain guides and teamriders from O'Neill & K2 the girls had two epic days in the mountains with lots of riding, safety training and hiking.
